      "created": 1783415081,
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "thinking",
          "thinking": "Let me analyze the department budgets vs. cumulative expenses:\n\n| Dept | Budget | Cumulative | Ratio | Status |\n|------|--------|-----------|-------|--------|\n| D001 投资银行部 | 230,395.17 | 363,614.58 | 1.58x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D002 固定收益部 | 107,785.42 | 164,928.12 | 1.53x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D003 财富管理部 | 109,772.07 | 174,150.67 | 1.59x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D004 研究所 | 264,890.39 | 408,832.95 | 1.54x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D005 机构业务部 | 278,540.94 | 433,442.76 | 1.56x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D006 运营管理部 | 340,961.75 | 530,241.29 | 1.56x | **EXCEEDED** |\n| D007 信息技术部 | 301,500.00 | 252,588.38 | 0.84x | OK |\n| D008 合规风控部 | 381,600.00 | 297,095.29 | 0.78x | OK |\n| D009 财务管理部 | 191,300.00 | 159,294.06 | 0.83x | OK |\n| D010 人力资源部 | 164,500.00 | 139,536.39 | 0.85x | OK |\n\nSo 6 departments (D001-D006) have exceeded their annual budgets. This is clearly a major finding.\n\nAccording to:\n- Article 13 of Expense Reimbursement Management (2025): \"部门年度预算不足时不得继续报销。预算使用达到预算额度的1.0倍后,确需发生的费用应履行专项审批。\"\n- Article 3 of Budget Management: \"部门费用累计使用达到年度预算额度的1.0倍后,原则上不得继续报销。\"\n\nBut wait - the task says \"只输出超标准专项结果\" which means \"only output special results that exceed standards\". And it's labeled as \"full_year_rule_audit\".\n\nLet me also check for other types of violations. Let me look at some specific expense records more closely.\n\nActually, since there are 4240 records, I should focus on what's most relevant. Let me look at the expense types and their specific limits:\n\n1. **Business entertainment (业务招待费)**: \n   - Single activity ≤ 5,000元 (Article 2)\n   - Per person ≤ 300元 (Article 3)\n   - Cannot split same visit/meeting (Article 4)\n\n2. **Training expense (培训费)**:\n   - Per person per session ≤ 3,500元 (Article 2)\n   - Internal training ≤ 800元/day (Article 3)\n   - External training ≤ 1,200元/day (Article 4)\n   - Training accommodation: Class 1 city 500元/night, Class 2 city 420元/night, Class 3 city 350元/night\n\n3. **Office supplies (办公用品)**:\n   - Per person per month ≤ 600元 (Article 2)\n\n4. **Communication (通讯费)**:\n   - Per person per month ≤ 300元 (Article 3)\n\n5. **Travel lodging (差旅住宿)**:\n   - Depends on level and city tier (Article 4)\n   - Employee: 450/380/300\n   - Manager: 650/550/450\n   - Dept head: 850/700/600\n   - Executive: 1100/900/750\n\n6. **Local transport (市内交通)**:\n   - Class 1 city: 120元/day\n   - Class 2 city: 100元/day\n   - Class 3 city: 80元/day\n\nThe task says \"只输出超标准专项结果\" - meaning I should output results that exceed standards in special/specific categories.\n\nSince it's a \"full_year_rule_audit\" (全年规则审计), the primary focus should be on annual budget overruns.\n\nLet me now check specific expense records that might show specific violations. Let me look at some records more carefully.\n\nLet me check if there are specific expense records that exceed the individual limits. Let me search for high-value expenses.",
          "signature": ""
        },
